        "name": "Unsettling Knowledge",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You share a piece of hidden knowledge with a creature that is both upsetting and intriguing. When you Cast this Spell, choose Arcana, Nature, Occultism, Religion, or Society as the focus of this knowledge. The target must attempt a Will save.",
